arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The Lapham and Van Wie files are arranged into two subseries:

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The Lapham and Van Wie files include field staff files from the Research and Evaluation Unit of the Population Council. Major topics include the evaluation of field programs, Gavin and Jones - Indonesia correspondence, records of the Taylor-Berelson Maternal and Child Health-Family Planning (MCH/FP) program, and research on fertility projection research.
